---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Framework | Identity Engineering">
	<main>
		<section class="min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col justify-center pt-24 pb-16">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
				<div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-cyan-400/70 mb-6">The Framework</div>
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-[0.95] mb-8">
					Identity Engineering
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/50 font-light max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
					A science-grounded model for understanding and designing human identity — built on principles from physics, information theory, and systems engineering.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Framework overview -->
		<section class="py-24 border-t border-white/10">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
				<div class="grid gap-20">

					<!-- Identity Stem -->
					<div>
						<div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-violet-400/60 mb-4">Foundation</div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">
							<a href="/identity-stem" class="hover:text-violet-300 transition">Identity Stem</a>
						</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							The temporal axis of identity. Past as State Differential, Present as State, Future as Vision Gradient. The stem is the backbone from which all other properties emerge.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Mass -->
					<div>
						<div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-violet-400/60 mb-4">01</div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Mass</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							The depth and substance of your personal and professional stake. Not volume — but density and weight. The heavier your identity mass, the stronger your gravitational pull on reality.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Curvature -->
					<div>
						<div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-cyan-400/60 mb-4">02</div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Curvature</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							How a strong vision warps what appears possible or inevitable. Like mass bends spacetime, identity mass bends the fabric of your reality — pulling opportunities toward your trajectory.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Gravitation -->
					<div>
						<div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-violet-400/60 mb-4">03</div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Gravitation</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							The attractive force of a coherent, owned vision. It pulls in opportunities, people, and energy — not by seeking, but by the sheer presence of your designed identity field.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Questions as Probes -->
					<div>
						<div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-cyan-400/60 mb-4">04</div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Questions as Probes</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							Precision instruments to measure and adjust the geometry of your identity. Each question is a probe sent into your reality — returning data about where you are and what's possible.
						</p>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="py-24 border-t border-white/10">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Go deeper</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-white/50 mb-10">
					Explore the frontier questions that push beyond the current framework.
				</p>
				<a href="/big-questions" class="px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/20 transition">
					Big Questions →
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
